---
import '../../assets/styles/global.css'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import personalGifts from '../../assets/images/index/owner-personal-handmade-gifts.JPG'
---


<section class="owner-story__section" id="about">
	<div class="owner-story__inner content-shell">
		<div class="owner-story__intro">
			<div class="owner-story__intro-content">
				<h2 class="owner-story__title">A home-based baker for celebrations that should taste as good as they look</h2>
				<div class="owner-story__body">
					<p>
						Perlette Cakes was built around a simple idea: celebration bakes should feel personal, generous, and genuinely delicious from the first slice to the last.
					</p>
					<p>
						We bake for birthdays, gatherings, gifting, and everyday milestones across Klang Valley, with the same care we would give to our own family table.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="owner-story__media">
				<Image
					src={personalGifts}
					alt="Personal handmade gifts made by Perlette Cakes as we prioritize quality over anything."
					loading="eager"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="owner-story__layout-notes">
			<div class="owner-story__notes">
				<div class="owner-story__note">
					<h3>Homemade, but assured</h3>
					<p>Each order is made to order, so the site should feel warm and personal without losing polish.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="owner-story__note">
					<h3>Taste comes first</h3>
					<p>Beautiful finishing matters, but the cake still needs to be the part guests go back for.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="owner-story__note">
					<h3>Delivery across Klang Valley</h3>
					<p>Orders are confirmed on WhatsApp and sent out through Lalamove rather than pickup.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.owner-story__section {
		padding-bottom: var(--bottom-space-section-md);
	}

	.owner-story__inner, .owner-story__intro {
		display: flex;
	}

	.owner-story__intro {
		width: 80%;
		display: flex;
	}

	.owner-story__title {
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		text-wrap: balance;
	}

	.owner-story__media {
		width: 80vw;
		display: flex;
		align-items:end;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.owner-story__media img {
		width: 80%;
		height: 80%;
	}

	.owner-story__intro-content {
		gap: var(--gap-space-md);
		max-width: 50rem;
		margin-right: var(--side-space-content-md);
		background-color: var(--pink-primary-bg);
		color: var(--white-text);
		padding: 40px 50px;
		align-self: flex-start;
	}

	.owner-story__intro-content h2 {
		padding-bottom: var(--bottom-space-header-md);
	}

	.owner-story__intro-content p {
		margin-bottom: var(--bottom-space-text-md);
	}

	.owner-story__body,
	.owner-story__notes {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-self: flex-end;
	}

	.owner-story__layout-notes {
		display: grid;
	}

	.owner-story__notes {
		gap: var(--gap-space-md);
	}

	.owner-story__note {
		padding: var(--space-lg);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
		background: var(--pink-primary-bg);
		color: var(--white-text);
	}

	.owner-story__note h3 {
		font-size: var(--header-three-font-size);
		margin-bottom: var(--bottom-space-header-md);
	}

	.owner-story__note p {
		color: var(--white-text);
	}

	@media (max-width: 100rem) {
		.owner-story__intro {
			width: 100%;
			display: flex;
		}

		.owner-story__layout-notes {
			display: none;
		}

		.owner-story__media img {
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 80rem) {
		.owner-story__intro-content {
			gap: var(--gap-space-md);
			width: 100%;
			align-self: center;
			margin-right: 0;
		}

		.owner-story__intro {
			width: 100%;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.owner-story__media {
			width: 100%;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			padding-top: ;
		}

		.owner-story__media img {
			width: 80%;
			padding: var(--top-space-media-md-mobile) 0;
		}
	}
</style>
